    "The indications for R E T R A C T E D A R T I C L E(LLM), GleamerAI cannot translate radiological image information into language or a precise classification system.",
    "Ope-nAI, an LLM that was officially launched in November 2022, can produce speech and has already demonstrated its ability to perform medical tasks, such as passing the United States Medical Licensing Examination (USMLE) [8].",
    "A previous study has demonstrated that chatbots utilising ChatGPT 4 technology are capable of producing AO codes from radiological reports.",
    "These were significantly faster, but much less accurate in the creation of AO codes [9].",
    "On 25 September 2023, the previously text-based language model ChatGPT 4 received an update for image input and processing."
